# Webex alert action settings

param.bot_token = <string>
* Cisco Webex Bot Token

param.room_id = <string>
* Cisco Webex Room Name or Room ID
* Can be either the room/space name (e.g., "Security Alerts") or the Room ID

param.message = <string>
* Message to send

param.message_type = <string>
* Message format: text or markdown

